name: Octo-Guacamole
body:
### Octo-Guacamole
Right now, there's a map editor and some basic tutorials. Use your controller to jump and bend your environment to get to the next puzzle!


### Gameplay
Puzzles - 5 right now, bound to be many more, with brain teasing, or maybe reflex-pushing jumpy-spinny-things.

### Level Editor
If I'm not good enough at puzzles for you, make your own (or find some) maps to try out.


### Authors and Contributors
Everything but sound (and creation of unity engine, controller images) @dasalvarp

### Contact?
Message me here or on twitter (@dasalvarp
